        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>residential districts [300000742], land use districts [300000724], districts by function [300000706], districts [300000705], Built Complexes and Districts (hierarchy name) [300000201], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
